Rethinking the principles of 21st century philanthropy

View this email in your browser (http://us10.campaign-archive1.com/?u=3D3f=
89269c6132144b6f1c5ce78&id=3Dae41af544d&e=3Da8a5b20bc3)

http://fordfoundation.us10.list-manage.com/track/click?u=3D3f89269c6132144=
